Class Attribute

java.lang.Object
  com.revolsys.gis.data.model.Attribute
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cloneable
Direct Known Subclasses:
AbstractFileGdbAttribute, FusionTablesAttribute, JdbcAttribute
public class Attribute
extends Object
implements Cloneable

The Attribute class defines the name, type and other properties about each attribute on a DataObject in the DataObjectMetaData.

Author:
Paul Austin
See Also:
DataObject, DataObjectMetaData
